import { Button, Grid, Input, PageHeader, Typography } from 'hero-design';
import React from 'react'
import { useTheme } from 'styled-components';


function Login() {

    return (
        <>
            <Grid>
                <Grid.Row style={{ margin: `10px`}}>
                    <Grid.Col span={[16, 16, 16, 16, 16]} offset={[4, 4, 4, 4, 4]}>
                        <PageHeader title="August digital asset management" />
                    </Grid.Col>
                </Grid.Row>
                <Grid.Row style={{ margin: `10px`}}>
                    <Grid.Col span={[16, 16, 16, 16, 16]} offset={[4, 4, 4, 4, 4]}>
                        <Input
                            placeholder="Please enter your user name"
                            size="large"
                        />
                        <Input
                            placeholder="Please enter your password"
                            size="large"
                        />
                    </Grid.Col>
                </Grid.Row>
                <Grid.Row style={{ margin: `10px`}}>
                    <Grid.Col span={[4, 4, 4, 4, 4]} offset={[18, 18, 18, 18, 18]}>
                        <Button variant="outlined"
                            intent="primary"
                            text="Large"
                            size="large">
                            Login
                        </Button>
                    </Grid.Col>

                </Grid.Row>
            </Grid>


        </>

    )
}

export default Login;
